quran[11]{c,v,t,f}:
  100,10,"tí wọ́n sì tú ohun tó wà nínú igbá-àyà ẹ̀dá síta pátápátá,"
  100,11,"dájúdájú Olúwa wọn ni Alámọ̀tán nípa wọn ní Ọjọ́ yẹn?"
  101,7,"ó sì máa wà nínú ìṣẹ̀mí tó máa yọ́nú sí."
  101,8,"Ní ti ẹni tí òṣùwọ̀n (iṣẹ́ rere) rẹ̀ bá sì fúyẹ́,"
  101,9,"Hāwiyah sì ni ibùgbé rẹ̀."
  102,4,"Lẹ́yìn náà, ní ti òdodo, láìpẹ́ ẹ máa mọ̀."
  102,5,"Ní ti òdodo, tí ó bá jẹ́ pé ẹ ni ìmọ̀ àmọ̀dájú ni (ẹ̀yin ìbá tí ṣe bẹ́ẹ̀)."
  102,6,"Dájúdájú ẹ máa rí iná Jẹhīm."
  103,1,"Allāhu fi àkókò ìrọ̀lẹ́ ayé búra."
  103,2,"Dájúdájú ènìyàn wà nínú òfò."
  103,3,"Àyàfi àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, tí wọ́n ṣe àwọn iṣẹ́ rere, tí wọ́n sọ àsọtẹ́lẹ̀ òdodo láààrin ara wọn, tí wọ́n sì tún sọ àsọtẹ́lẹ̀ sùúrù láààrin ara wọn."